      "class": "Evidence",
      "entity_id": null,
      "paper_id": "PMC_UNKNOWN",
      "text_span_id": "radiation_6",
      "text": "It has been demonstrated that patients with LFS who receive radiation therapy have an increased risk of radiation-related malignancies within irradiated areas. The reported risk of developing radiation-induced malignancy ranges from 15% to 35% in the modern literature.",
