  "notes": [
    "This case report describes a complex genetic evaluation involving mosaic TP53 variant and its implications for Li-Fraumeni syndrome diagnosis and management.",
    "The patient had multiple breast tumors (bilateral DCIS and malignant phyllodes tumor) which supported the mosaic TP53 diagnosis.",
    "Variant allele frequency analysis of tumor samples was crucial for confirming mosaicism."
